                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250519-61-off363 t18250519-61-crimeloc365"></join>, three silver spoons, value 5 l., and a silver sauce ladle, value 15 s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18250519-61-victim385" type="victimName">
                        Anthony 
                        Bacon
                     <interp inst="t18250519-61-victim385" type="surname" value="Bacon"></interp>
